|                     File| Frequency|
+------------------------------------+
|                  RESTART|       500|
|           PARAVIEW_ASCII|       500|
+------------------------------------+
Writing the convergence history file every 1 inner iterations.
Writing the screen convergence history every 100 inner iterations.
The tabular file format is CSV (.csv).
Convergence history file name: results/history.
Forces breakdown file name: forces_breakdown.dat.
Surface file name: surface.
Volume file name: vol_solution.
Restart file name: results/restart.dat.

